係因為非呢個女仔不可，你就繼續努力啦，用盡你嘅一切方法去挽回佢，lur地又好跪地又好，無論結果如何，都唔好俾自己後悔。<br />\n<br />\n加油"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T17:13:16.000Z","msg":"我諗我係前者<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"01da285ba14dee14b511a189836e7a473de8b413","tid":2347030,"uid":59370,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T19:20:27.000Z","msg":"你set個時限俾自己，你鍾意嘅都可以同對方講，話大家試下相處一個月，如果感情返晒黎咪無事，如果唔得，咁感情就無得勉強，努力完唔得就放手啦。"},{"pid":"ea196124fec6b387b7e327ac04b5a2ae5f61ed1e","tid":2347030,"uid":275797,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T19:24:54.000Z","msg":"唉<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n講真 愛好兩極"},{"pid":"0bfd29aab1b4b4fc2e200e38dc6ee0617809c244","tid":2347030,"uid":161251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T19:54:37.000Z","msg":"感建分"},{"pid":"ef8c547e65a6aee4d1e2b12fefd98b3f1c48a62d","tid":2347030,"uid":224831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fac49b7425f21ad138ccd3bc865e402ae2355432","tid":2347030,"uid":271223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:54:26.000Z","msg":"當初分手見到你一個人過得咁開心、我就諗大家分開會比較好<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n後來你叫我追返你、但係又要我比時間你適應返兩個人、依加仲辛苦過岩岩分開個陣<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T20:11:42.000Z","msg":"咁你地依加算係咩關係？？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/surprise.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"349da3dd03115f5f18914ea6ff36eb5beed35bdf","tid":2347030,"uid":271223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ef8c547e65a6aee4d1e2b12fefd98b3f1c48a62d","tid":2347030,"uid":224831,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"fac49b7425f21ad138ccd3bc865e402ae2355432","tid":2347030,"uid":271223,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-30T16:54:26.